name: Around Football: Red Tribune
description:
A red flare lights up beside me. It was a friendly game between Persebaya Surabaya against PSS Sleman, titled Game of Celebration. Persebaya, the host of this game won by two goals to one. And when the whistle blown at the end of the match, the stadium turns in to a fiery red thanks to those flare.
